────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
STORIES (separately licensed)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The story content files (whispering-forest.json, hollow-forest.json,
saltbound.json, and any future bundled stories) are creative content, not
Software. Each story declares its own `creative_license` field inside the
JSON; that field is authoritative for distribution and derivative-work
permissions of the story content itself.

Players are explicitly permitted to author and distribute their own story
JSON files for use with the Engine, under any license they choose. The
Engine is the platform; user-authored stories are content that runs on it.

